<p>Your Google Business Profile is the single most important ranking factor for local search. It accounts for 32% of local pack ranking influence, according to the <a href="https://whitespark.ca/local-search-ranking-factors/">2026 Whitespark Local Search Ranking Factors survey</a>. 8 of the top 10 local ranking signals come directly from your profile.</p>
